bilingual.source: I'm not going to swim at the pool.
Look at the swimming pool and the huge sports ground.
bilingual.target: 看看游泳池和巨大的运动场。

bilingual.source: They gathered round the swimming pool and cheered her on.
bilingual.target: 他们围在游泳池周围，给她加油。

bilingual.source: How can you learn to swim without going to a pool?
bilingual.target: 你不去游泳池怎么学游泳？

bilingual.source: Last week I was walking to the swimming pool with my friends.
bilingual.target: 上周我和朋友们一起走去游泳池。

bilingual.source: His family is very rich and his house has got a swimming pool.
bilingual.target: 他的家庭很富有，他的房子有一个游泳池。

list.abstract: Pool（英 [puːl]，美 [puːl]），英语单词。作名词时指池塘；池；共用车辆。作动词时指积成池；把（钱或其他资金）集中共用；使受牵连。短语搭配有wading pool（戏水池）。例句有“You weigh about 90% less in the pool.（你在泳池里的体重减轻了90%。）” Pool的近义词有billiard ball。

yingyinNormal.en: No, as soon as something opens up we'll move right in. Unless it doesn't have a pool, I need a pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，只要有公寓招租，我们马上搬进去，如果附带游泳池的话，我需要游泳池。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. There are gonna be some pasty folks by the pool tomorrow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，明天游泳池旁一定有许多苍白的人。

yingyinNormal.en: AC is zonked, babe, we're gonna have to call someone. Pool, huh? Not a movie? Are you sure you're okay with the pool today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 空调完全挂了，得找人来修。去游泳对吗，不看电影？确定你今天能去游泳池吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And I am happy to report that he died peacefully in his sleep, drunk at the bottom of a pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很高兴地通知你，他已经喝高，在游泳池底长眠了。

yingyinNormal.en: You had a key to the pool? All right, what happened to being beyond this? Sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有去游泳池的钥匙？好了，一直说这个有什么用。不好意思。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll just go for a little walk. Good morning, Mr. Pig. I see you have found the swimming pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去散散步。早上好，猪先生，我看你已经找到游泳池了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll just go for a little walk. Ah. Good morning, Mr. Pig. I see you have found the swimming pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去散散步。早上好，猪先生，我看你已经找到游泳池了。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I think, Ross already has one. Yeah, that guy's finally gonna be able to put in that pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想罗斯已经有一个了。对，那家伙总算可以有足够的资金盖游泳池了。

yingyinNormal.en: What is it to be? Car park? Swimming pool? Rocket station ? A house. Can you build it exactly like this please? But bigger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想造什么？停车场？游泳池？火箭站？一座房子！请按照这个模型造就可以了。但是要大一点。

yingyinNormal.en: There's also a bar pool, five international restaurants, a spa, a fitness center, a nightclub and, of course, the beach and beach clubs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还设有酒吧，游泳池，五个国际餐厅和一个温泉疗养中心，健身中心和夜总会，当然还有海滨和沙滩俱乐部。

yingyinNormal.en: It was built by captain Francis Fowke in 1896. He also designed the museum of natural history. It was purely a fan of big, overbearing swimming pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是弗兰西斯·福克船长1896年建造的，他还设计了自然历史博物馆。这简直像是一个巨大的游泳池。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, Mr. Pig. What is it to be? Car park? Swimming pool? Rocket station ? A house. Can you build it exactly like this please? But bigger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，猪先生！你想造什么？停车场？游泳池？火箭站？一座房子！请按照这个模型造就可以了。但是要大一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Nah, I can't. I got to pick up my mom from her water aerobics class. 18 overweight women flapping their arm fat in a swimming pool. Looks like the manatee tank at Sea World.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不行，我要去水中有氧运动班接我妈。十八个超重妇女在游泳池里甩着肥大的手臂，就像海洋世界里的海牛。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George love their paddling pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩佩和乔治喜欢他们的戏水池。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George love their paddling pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩琪和乔治喜欢充气泳池。

yingyinNormal.en: It is George's first time at a swimming pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这次乔治第一次下水游泳。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and her family are at the swimming pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和家人一起去游泳。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, but after that, we're shooting some pool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，不过之后要打球。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a big concrete swimming pool with a concrete cover.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个有混凝土保护层的大水泥泳池。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Senior year of college, on a pool table. Pool table? That's my sister.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大四在桌球台上。桌球台上？这就是我妹啦。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a small deep body of usually fresh water

examination_example.sentence: The compositions often seem to represent attempts to call forth the spirit of plant life, through an introduction of colors and small <highlight>pools</highlight> of water.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些作品以引入色彩和小水池的方式，看起来象征着唤起植物生命的精神。

sense_info_list.en: a group of people available for work when required or considered as a resource

examination_example.sentence: Increasing opportunities for board membership without increasing the <highlight>pool</highlight> of qualified women to serve on such boards has led to a "golden skirt" phenomenon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 增加董事会成员的席位，却没有更多称职的女性能为董事会工作，这导致了“金裙”现象。

sense_info_list.en: a small, shallow patch of liquid lying on a surface
a supply of vehicles or goods available for use when needed
(of two or more people or organizations) put money or other assets into a common fund
the collective amount of players' stakes in gambling or sweepstakes
a game of billiards played on a table with six pockets
a small body of standing liquid

word_usage.usage:
pool原意是指“水塘；池塘”，引申为“(金钱、资源或思想等的)汇集；集中；备用”。例：
In turn, that created a pool of labour for factories. 
反过来，这又为工厂创造了大量的劳动力。

sense_info_list.en: a small deep body of usually fresh water

examination_example.sentence: Probing the rock <highlight>pools</highlight> of a local beach or practising French on a language exchange can fire children's passions, boost their skills.

examination_example.sentence: Methods such as whole school fund raising, with the proceeds (收益) <highlight>pooled</highlight>, can help to extend opportunities and fuel community spirit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如全校筹集资金并集中收益的方法，可以帮助扩大机会并激发社会精神。

sense_info_list.en: a game of billiards played on a table with six pockets

examination_example.sentence: Playing <highlight>pool</highlight>, playing cards, having dinner, having lunch, all work better than going through a survey of questions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 玩台球，打牌，吃晚饭，吃午餐比进行问题调查要好得多。

examination_example.sentence: You weigh about 90% less in the <highlight>pool</highlight>.
